channel.title: Web Developers
channel.description:
It sickens me to see everyone who claims that their a web developer can only make free forums from like SMFFree or Forumotion. Like bro, you aren't a web developer. I highly doubt you even know what HTML is or <div>. Congratulations that you can open a template from [i]freewebtemplates.com[/i] in notepad or Dreamweaver and you edit it. Half of the so called "web developers" are just skids that steal someones template and claim it as their own. This really needs to stop...
Anyone share the same thoughts as the above?
